<p>John and Dave kick off October with this great show talking about how to set up a dual Time Machine setup, tweaking your junk mail settings, fixing apps that don&rsquo;t want to run, sleeping an iMac with insomnia, and more! Download today &mdash; it&rsquo;s free &mdash; and enjoy!</p>
